{"id":7528,"date":"2023-06-29T08:28:00","date_gmt":"2023-06-29T14:28:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/?p=7528"},"modified":"2023-08-24T08:31:31","modified_gmt":"2023-08-24T14:31:31","slug":"rochester-hills-district-raises-30k-for-esophageal-cancer-association","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/news\/rochester-hills-district-raises-30k-for-esophageal-cancer-association\/","title":{"rendered":"ROCHESTER HILLS DISTRICT RAISES $30K+ FOR ESOPHAGEAL CANCER ASSOCIATION"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Harlan Electric Hosts 3rd Annual Charity Golf Tournament <\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap\">The Harlan Electric, Rochester Hills district held its Third Annual Charity Golf Tournament at Mystic Creek Golf Club on Monday, June 29<sup>th, <\/sup>benefitting <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ecaware.org\/\">Esophageal Cancer Awareness Association<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"alignright size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.harlanelectric.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-1-1600x1200.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7524\" width=\"347\" height=\"259\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-1-1600x1200.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-1-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-1.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 347px) 100vw, 347px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>The cause was a personal one, dedicated to our friend Chris Cichon whom we lost to esophageal cancer last summer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Chris was a true friend, an IBEW brother, an amazing father of four, and an incredibly loving husband. Chris gave 100% toward every aspect of his life. We wanted to honor him to help increase awareness of Esophageal Cancer and keep those that truly are the best of us around a little longer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Through the generous support of our employees, sponsors, customers, friends, and family, we proudly raised and donated more than $30,000 to Esophageal Cancer Awareness Association. The contribution supports EC Aware\u2019s mission to&nbsp;<strong>provide outreach<\/strong>&nbsp;for esophageal cancer patients, caregivers, and survivors, to<strong>&nbsp;increase public awareness<\/strong>&nbsp;of this disease, and to&nbsp;<strong>offer education and information<\/strong>&nbsp;in a supportive environment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Thank you to all our sponsors, participants, and employees for your continued generosity and support. Without you, this event would not have been possible!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-id=\"7525\" src=\"https:\/\/www.harlanelectric.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-2-1600x1200.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7525\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-2-1600x1200.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-2.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-id=\"7526\" src=\"https:\/\/www.harlanelectric.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-3-1600x1200.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7526\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-3-1600x1200.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-3-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-3-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-3-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-3.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-id=\"7527\" src=\"https:\/\/www.harlanelectric.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-4-1600x1200.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7527\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-4-1600x1200.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-4-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-4-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-4-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3rd-Annual-Charity-Golf-Tournament_HEC_2023-4.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Harlan Electric Hosts 3rd Annual Charity Golf Tournament The Harlan Electric, Rochester Hills district held its Third Annual Charity Golf Tournament at Mystic Creek Golf Club on Monday, June 29th, benefitting Esophageal Cancer Awareness Association. The cause was a personal one, dedicated to our friend Chris Cichon whom we lost to esophageal cancer last summer. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":16,"featured_media":7527,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[93],"class_list":["post-7528","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-community-involvement","subsidiary-harlan-electric"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7528"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/16"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7528"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7528\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":7531,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7528\/revisions\/7531"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7527"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7528"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7528"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templ